section.heading: State contribution for baseball stadium limited

content.p: Print RCWs > Title 82 > Chapter 82.14 > Section 82.14.0486 82.14.0485 << 82.14.0486 >> 82.14.049 PDF RCW 82.14.0486 State contribution for baseball stadium limited. Sections 101 through 105, chapter 1, Laws of 1995 3rd sp. sess. constitute the entire state contribution for a baseball stadium, as defined in RCW 82.14.0485 . The state will not make any additional contributions based on revised cost or revenue estimates, cost overruns, unforeseen circumstances, or any other reason. [ 1995 3rd sp.s. c 1 s 106 .] NOTES: Part headings not law — Effective date — 1995 3rd sp.s. c 1: See notes following RCW 82.14.0485 .
